<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>{{ title }} — Indie Creator Toolkit</title>
<meta name="description" content="{{ description }}">
<link rel="canonical" href="{{ canonical }}">
<meta property="og:title" content="{{ title }}">
<meta property="og:description" content="{{ description }}">
<meta property="og:type" content="article">
<style>
  body { font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; max-width: 760px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 1rem; line-height: 1.6; color: #222; }
  h1, h2, h3 { line-height: 1.25; }
  h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
  table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 1rem 0; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  th, td { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.5rem; text-align: left; }
  th { background: #f6f6f6; }
  a { color: #0a66c2; }
  .meta { color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem; }
  .disclosure { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666; border: 1px solid #eee; padding: 0.6rem; border-radius: 6px; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  nav { font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  footer { margin-top: 3rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; color: #888; font-size: 0.85rem; }
  .pill { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 999px; background: #eef; font-size: 0.75rem; margin-right: 4px; }
  .free { background: #e0f5e0; }
  .paid { background: #fde8e8; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav><a href="../">← Indie Creator Toolkit</a></nav>
<article>
  <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
  <p class="meta">Updated {{ updated }} · {{ word_count }} words · {{ persona_label }}</p>
  <div class="disclosure">⚠ Some links are affiliate links — at no extra cost to you, we earn a small commission if you sign up. We only recommend tools we'd use ourselves.</div>
  {{ body | safe }}
</article>
<footer>
  <p>Indie Creator Toolkit · Updated automatically · <a href="https://github.com/{{ gh_user }}/indie-creator-toolkit">source</a></p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
